# 🧠 Decision Tree Navigator - VIRTUNEXA Edition

An interactive, responsive decision tree application designed for troubleshooting and learning purposes. Built with **HTML**, **CSS**, **JavaScript**, and **Bootstrap**, it features animated UI transitions and a sliding "VIRTUNEXA" banner for a modern, engaging experience.

---

## 🚀 Features

- 🌐 Clean, modern UI with gradient background
- 🧭 Dynamic decision tree navigation
- ✅ Smooth transitions and responsive design
- 🏷️ Animated sliding "VIRTUNEXA" banner
- 💡 Easy to expand with custom decision trees

---

## 🛠️ Technologies Used

- HTML5 & CSS3
- Bootstrap 5
- JavaScript (Vanilla)
- Custom animations with CSS

